# Windrose Modding Rule

- Read `README.md` and `docs/REPO_STRUCTURE.md` for repository conventions.
- Read `mods/boar-loot/docs/AI_HANDOFF.md` before making changes.
- Use `modding_tools/windrose_mod_cli.py` commands as the default workflow.
- Treat `.local/boar-loot.build.json` as the source of truth for local build/install.
- Keep staged paths mount-correct:
  - plugin content: `input/staged/R5/Plugins/R5BusinessRules/Content/...`
  - game content: `input/staged/Game/...`
- Prefer `build-install --backup-first` before testing.
- When successful workflows change, update:
  - `mods/boar-loot/docs/AI_HANDOFF.md`
  - `mods/boar-loot/README.md` (if user-facing steps changed)
  - `README.md` (if repository workflow changed)
